  "texts": [
    "Students were also keen on recommending AI games to their friends (Voulgari et al., 2021).",
    "Therefore, a combination of play/game-based and project-based approaches may consolidate AI concepts through gameplay while enhancing students' engagement in AI projects (Han et al., 2018).",
    "Students' level of satisfaction was found to be positively influenced by constructivist (e.g., project-based) and reflective (e.g., learning by design and learning by teaching) pedagogies (Ho et al., 2019; Shamir & Levin, 2021, 2022).",
    "In Lin et al. (2020), students reported a high satisfaction level upon acquiring AI knowledge.",
    "Their computational thinking and subsequent project performance were also enhanced."
  ],
